        <div class="firefly-howto container s-spacing-top xl-spacing-bottom xl-spacing-tablet xl-spacing-desktop static-links seo con-block" data-block-status="loaded"><div class="foreground"><div class="firefly-howto-item "><h3 class="firefly-howto-header"><button class="firefly-howto-trigger" id="btn-open-firefly" aria-expanded="false" type="button" aria-controls="panel-open-firefly" daa-ll="open-open-firefly"><span class="step-indicator">Step 1 </span><span class="firefly-howto-title">Open Firefly.</span><span class="firefly-howto-icon"><svg aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line class="vert-line" x1="12" y1="5" x2="12" y2="19"></line><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"></line></svg></span></button></h3><div class="firefly-howto-panel" id="panel-open-firefly"><div class="firefly-howto-panel-inner"><div class="firefly-howto-content"><p>Log in to <a href="https://firefly.adobe.com/">Firefly</a> and navigate to the <strong>Generate</strong> tab. Choose <strong>Generate Video</strong> or explore additional video features.</p></div></div></div></div><div class="firefly-howto-item "><h3 class="firefly-howto-header"><button class="firefly-howto-trigger" id="btn-choose-an-ai-model" aria-expanded="false" type="button" aria-controls="panel-choose-an-ai-model" daa-ll="open-choose-an-ai-model"><span class="step-indicator">Step 2 </span><span class="firefly-howto-title">Choose an AI model.</span><span class="firefly-howto-icon"><svg aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line class="vert-line" x1="12" y1="5" x2="12" y2="19"></line><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"></line></svg></span></button></h3><div class="firefly-howto-panel" id="panel-choose-an-ai-model"><div class="firefly-howto-panel-inner"><div class="firefly-howto-content"><p>From the dropdown menu, choose the Firefly video model or a partner model such as Google Veo, Sora, or Pika.</p></div></div></div></div><div class="firefly-howto-item "><h3 class="firefly-howto-header"><button class="firefly-howto-trigger" id="btn-write-a-text-prompt-or-upload-an-image" aria-expanded="false" type="button" aria-controls="panel-write-a-text-prompt-or-upload-an-image" daa-ll="open-write-a-text-prompt-or-upload-an-image"><span class="step-indicator">Step 3 </span><span class="firefly-howto-title">Write a text prompt or upload an image.</span><span class="firefly-howto-icon"><svg aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line class="vert-line" x1="12" y1="5" x2="12" y2="19"></line><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"></line></svg></span></button></h3><div class="firefly-howto-panel" id="panel-write-a-text-prompt-or-upload-an-image"><div class="firefly-howto-panel-inner"><div class="firefly-howto-content"><p>Your prompt should include style, angle, shot distance, effects, color grading, subject(s), and any other elements or descriptors to generate video that matches your vision. You can also upload an image that you want Firefly to put to motion. In this case, you should also use the text prompt to describe how you want the image brought to life.</p></div></div></div></div><div class="firefly-howto-item "><h3 class="firefly-howto-header"><button class="firefly-howto-trigger" id="btn-generate-your-video" aria-expanded="false" type="button" aria-controls="panel-generate-your-video" daa-ll="open-generate-your-video"><span class="step-indicator">Step 4 </span><span class="firefly-howto-title">Generate your video.</span><span class="firefly-howto-icon"><svg aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line class="vert-line" x1="12" y1="5" x2="12" y2="19"></line><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"></line></svg></span></button></h3><div class="firefly-howto-panel" id="panel-generate-your-video"><div class="firefly-howto-panel-inner"><div class="firefly-howto-content"><p>When you’re satisfied with your prompt, click Generate. The AI generated video results will appear shortly. If you like the video, use the Download button in the top right to download as an mp4 file.</p></div></div></div></div><div class="firefly-howto-item "><h3 class="firefly-howto-header"><button class="firefly-howto-trigger" id="btn-refine-revise-and-regenerate" aria-expanded="false" type="button" aria-controls="panel-refine-revise-and-regenerate" daa-ll="open-refine-revise-and-regenerate"><span class="step-indicator">Step 5 </span><span class="firefly-howto-title">Refine, revise, and regenerate.</span><span class="firefly-howto-icon"><svg aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line class="vert-line" x1="12" y1="5" x2="12" y2="19"></line><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"></line></svg></span></button></h3><div class="firefly-howto-panel" id="panel-refine-revise-and-regenerate"><div class="firefly-howto-panel-inner"><div class="firefly-howto-content"><p>Play with settings to explore different variations. In the panel on the left, you can adjust the aspect ratio, camera angle, and motion. And if you’d like, add more detail to your text prompt to generate completely new videos. Just be sure to save any videos you like before you create new ones.</p></div></div></div></div><div class="firefly-howto-item "><h3 class="firefly-howto-header"><button class="firefly-howto-trigger" id="btn-download-or-share-ai-generated-video" aria-expanded="false" type="button" aria-controls="panel-download-or-share-ai-generated-video" daa-ll="open-download-or-share-ai-generated-video"><span class="step-indicator">Step 6 </span><span class="firefly-howto-title">Download or share AI-generated video.</span><span class="firefly-howto-icon"><svg aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line class="vert-line" x1="12" y1="5" x2="12" y2="19"></line><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"></line></svg></span></button></h3><div class="firefly-howto-panel" id="panel-download-or-share-ai-generated-video"><div class="firefly-howto-panel-inner"><div class="firefly-howto-content"><p>Once you’re happy with your text-to-video AI project, it’s easy to download it directly to your computer or mobile device or share it with others for feedback. For further refinement, take your project to the <a href="/products/firefly/features/ai-video-editor/">AI video editor</a> to cut, trim, and rearrange video and audio clips on a simple layered timeline. Firefly makes exporting and sharing high-quality results simple — no technical skills required.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div>
